%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20freeze%20on%20foreign%20assistance%2C%20Weeks%20worries%20that%20America's%20soft%20power%20will%20suffer.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20worries%20that%20foreign%20aid%20cuts%20risk%20ceding%20influence%20to%20China%20and%20Russia%20in%20strategic%20regions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20public%20health%20in%20the%20early%2090s%20when%20a%20childhood%20friend%20was%20living%20with%20AIDS%2C%20and%20I%20took%20classes%20to%20learn%20more.%20My%20eyes%20were%20opened%20to%20how%20public%20health%20can%20transform%20communities%20and%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%2025%20years%2C%20I've%20worked%20to%20support%20US%20foreign%20assistance%20in%20global%20public%20health%20%E2%80%94%20most%20recently%20for%20DAI%2C%20one%20of%20USAID's%20largest%20contractors.%20Through%20my%20work%2C%20I've%20witnessed%20firsthand%20how%20American%20foreign%20assistance%20has%20transformed%20lives%20abroad%20while%20making%20our%20nation%20safer%20and%20stronger%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20USAID%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarco-rubio-announces-official-end-of-most-usaid-programs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20transitional%20moment%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20what's%20next%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20Due%20to%20the%20current%20administration's%20halts%20on%20foreign%20assistance%2C%20our%20work%20at%20DAI%20has%20been%20paused.%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-elon-musk-usaid-funding-freeze-layoffs-furloughs-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrently%20furloughed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20my%20entire%20team%20and%20hundreds%20of%20colleagues%2C%20with%20very%20little%20notice.%20I%20lost%20my%20paycheck%20January%2031%20and%20my%20health%20insurance%20March%2031.%20USAID%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-di