22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20would%20typically%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20rent%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20But%20many%20residents%20have%20chosen%20to%20stay%20even%20after%20raising%20their%20Series%20A%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20ultimately%20the%20reason%20that%20people%20stay%2C%20even%20though%20maybe%20they%20could%20live%20in%20a%20nicer%20place%2C%20is%20just%20a%20really%20strong%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shmulyan.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20house%20where%20people%20are%20doing%20their%20life's%20work%2C%20and%20doing%20it%20side%20by%20side%20with%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mission%20Control%20is%20one%20of%20San%20Francisco's%20oldest%20hacker%20houses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68018eeca466d2b74ab38750%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMission%20Control%20is%20one%20of%20San%20Francisco's%20oldest%20hacker%20houses.%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20walked%20upstairs%2C%20a%20dozen%20current%20and%20former%20residents%20were%20bunched%20together%20in%20the%20living%20room%2C%20sipping%20Diet%20Cokes%20and%20coding%20on%20their%20MacBooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECOVID%20proved%20people%20can%20work%20from%20anywhere%2C%20but%20far%20from%20making%20hacker%20houses%20like%20this%20one%20obsolete%2C%20the%20residents%20here%20said%20the%20pandemic%20made%20them%20more%20in%20demand%20than%20ever%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20outside%20world%20has%20become%20more%20unstable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20natural%20human%20instinct%20to%20find%20connections%20when%20there's%20confusion%20and%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chase%20Changhee%20Seon%2C%20who%20came%20to%20Mission%20Control%20from%20Seoul%20to%20start%20an%20events%20and%20community%20platform.%20%26quot%3BEven%20in%20this%20world%20of%20tech%20and%20AI%2C%20you%20cannot%20replace%20human%20connections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20at%20Mission%20Control%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68018f48c6ad288d147e84b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECleaners%20come%20once%20a%20week%20to%20Mission%20Control.%3Cp%3EBen%20Bergman%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%206400-square-foot%20interior%20somewhat%20resembles%20a%20frat%20house%2C%20with%20a%20random%20bench%20press%20no%20one%20seems%20to%20use%20in%20the%20hallway%20and%20mismatched%20furniture%20that%20has%20seen%20better%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20key%20differences.%20There%20are%20no%20TVs%2C%20and%20everything%20from%20the%20kitchen%20to%20the%20bathrooms%20is%20immaculately%20clean%20thanks%20to%20cleaners%20who%20come%20every%20week.%20And%20almost%20no%20one%20in%20the%20house%20drinks%20any%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20party%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Brennan-Burke%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20drink%20tea%2C%20build%20stuff%2C%20and%20hang%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2206bb84c2-361f-439f-a68c-1cc8fd13e156%5C%22%3ENo%20influencers%2C%20please%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20cold%20application%20to%20get%20into%20Mission%20Control.%20You%20have%20to%20know%20someone%20in%20the%20house%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20advocate%20for%20you%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20the%20odds%20are%20long%2C%20with%20less%20than%203%25%20of%20prospects%20making%20it%20through%20the%20extensive%20interview%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20met%20residents%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20learn%20how%20many%20are%20not%20currently%20working%20on%20any%20startup%2C%20and%20the%20interview%20criteria%20reflect%20that.%20Who%20you%20are%20and%20whether%20you%20seem%20like%20you%20will%20vibe%20with%20the%20other%20inhabitan