.%20In%202013%2C%20Northrup%20Grumman's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.northropgrumman.com%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fair%2Fx-47b-ucas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX-47B%20demonstrator%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20launched%20from%20and%20landed%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20the%20USS%20George%20H.%20W.%20Bush%2C%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20General%20Atomics'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ga-asi.com%2Fremotely-piloted-aircraft%2Fgray-eagle-stol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGray%20Eagle%20STOL%3C%2Fa%3E%20UAV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twz.com%2Fair%2Fgray-eagle-stol-drone-flies-from-south-korean-amphibious-assault-ship%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etook%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20South%20Korean%20amphibious%20assault%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20before%20those%20two%2C%20the%20US%20Navy's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-making-plans-to-load-aircraft-carriers-with-drones-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETDN-1%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20demonstrated%20the%20ability%20to%20take%20off%20from%20carriers%20in%201944.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20efforts%20were%20largely%20tests%20or%20one-offs.%20The%20concept%20of%20a%20drone%20carrier%20goes%20well%20beyond%3A%20a%20ship%20with%20a%20large%20flight%20deck%20designed%20to%20launch%20waves%20of%20drones%2C%20much%20like%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20sorties%20piloted%20aircraft.%20In%20essence%2C%20it%20is%20a%20dedicated%2C%20purpose-built%20drone%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20disagreement%20over%20which%20country%20has%20technically%20built%20the%20first%20drone%20carrier%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20the%20debate%20over%20who%20built%20the%20first%20aircraft%20carrier%20in%20the%20early%2020%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20century.%20And%20the%20contestants%20in%20this%20race%20are%20countries%20that%20haven't%20traditionally%20been%20the%20world's%20leading%20global%20navies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203880bb6-f167-4b6d-9b3b-219fa7ee6ecc%5C%22%3ETurkey's%20drone-carrying%20flagship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20repurposed%20its%20new%20flagship%2C%20TCG%20Anadolu%2C%20into%20a%20drone%20carrier%20with%20fixed-wing%20aircraft%20from%20Baykar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f569393fe8d39283627864%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurkey%20repurposed%20its%20new%20flagship%2C%20TCG%20Anadolu%2C%20into%20a%20drone%20carrier%20with%20fixed-wing%20aircraft%20from%20Baykar.%3Cp%3EMC2%20Jackson%20Adkins%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETurkey%20is%20the%20first%20country%20to%20claim%20the%20commissioning%20of%20a%20drone%20carrier.%20Ordered%20in%202015%2C%20launched%20in%202018%2C%20and%20commissioned%20in%202023%2C%20TCG%20Anadolu%20is%20757%20feet%20long%20and%20displaces%2027%2C436%20tons.%20It%20is%20the%20Turkish%20Navy's%20most%20advanced%20vessel%20and%20current%20flagship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Turkish%20government%20claims%2070%25%20of%20Anadolu%20was%20built%20with%20domestic%20components%2C%20the%20ship's%20design%20is%20that%20of%20Spain's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seaforces.org%2Fmarint%2FSpanish-Navy%2FAmphibious-Ship%2FL-61-SPS-Juan-Carlos-I.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuan%20Carlos%20I%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20its%20Spanish%20forebear%2C%20Anadolu%20was%20originally%20intended%20to%20carry%20an%20air%20wing%20of%20helicopters%20and%20manned%20short%20take-off%20and%20vertical%20landing%20(STOVL)%20jets%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20American%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fequipment%2Ff-35b-lightning-ii%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-35B%3C%2Fa%3E%20stealth%20strike%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202019%2C%20Turkey%20was%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20F-35%20program%20due%20to%20its%20purchase%20of%20Russian-made%20S-400%20surface-to-air%20missile%20systems%2C%20which%20US%20and%20NATO%20officials%20worried%20could%20be%20used%20to%20gather%20intelligence%20on%20the%20F-35.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20limit%20Anadolu's%20air%20wing%20to%20just%20helicopters%2C%20the%20Turks%20opted%20to%20repurpose%20the%20ship%20into%20the%20world's%20first%20drone%20carrier%2C%20relying%20on%20its%20world-class%20drone%20industry%20to%20provide%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bayraktar%20TB3%20drone%20took%20off%20and%20landed%20from%20the%20TCG%20Anadolu%20in%20November.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f569a73fe8d39283627877%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221294%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bayraktar%20TB3%20drone%20took%20off%20and%20landed%20from%20the%20TCG%20Anadolu%20in%20November.%3Cp%3EBaykar%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20drone%20models%20will%20operate%20from%20the%20Anadolu%3A%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbaykartech.com%2Fen%2Fuav%2Fbayraktar-tb3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBayraktar%20TB3%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbaykartech.com%2Fen%2Fuav%2Fbayraktar-kizilelma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBayraktar%20K%C4%B1z%C4%B1lelma%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Both%20were%20developed%20by%20the%20well-known%20maker%20Baykar.%20The%20TB3%20is%20a%20navalized%20variant%20of%20the%20company's%20combat-proven%20propeller-driven%20TB2%20drone%20that%20features%20folding%20wings%2C%20a%20strengthened%20suspension%2C%20and%20a%20more%20powerful%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaykar%20says%20it%20has%20an%20endurance%20of%20over%2021%20hours%20and%20can%20carry%20up%20to%20617%20pounds%20of%20ordnance.%20It%20can%20be%20used%20for%20both%20surveillance%20and%20strike%20missions%2C%20especially%20against%20enemies%20with%20no%20or%20low-tier%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaykar%20describes%20the%20K%C4%B1z%C4%B1lelma%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfighter%20UAV%26quot%3B%20that%20features%20a%20turbofan%20jet%20engine%20enabling%20it%20to%20reach%20a%20max%20speed%20of%20Mach%200.9%20and%20fly%20as%20high%20as%2045%2C000%20feet.%20It%20can%20also%20carry%203%2C300%20pounds%20of%20weapons%20on%20external%20hardpoints%20and%20in%20internal%20weapons%20bays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurkish%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Anadolu's%20air%20wing%20will%20be%20composed%20of%2012%20unmanned%20combat%20aircraft.%20The%20ship%20can%20also%20carry%20AH-1W%20Cobra%20and%20T129%20attack%20helicopters%20and%20SH-60B%20Seahawks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20TB3%20made%20history%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbaykartech.com%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fa-first-in-the-history-of-global-aviation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccessfully%20taking%20off%20from%20and%20landing%20on%20the%20TCG%20Anadolu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20fixed-wing%20drone%20to%20take%20off%20and%20land%20on%20a%20short-deck%20ship.%20In%20January%2C%20a%20TB3%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbaykartech.com%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fbayraktar-tb3-its-armed%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccessfully%20conducted%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20first%20strike%20against%20a%20mock%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278637543-aab3-429b-9ec4-ba62c8368540%5C%22%3EIran's%20drone%20carrier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iran's%20Shahid%20Bahman%20Bagheri%20is%20a%20former%20container%20ship%20converted%20into%20a%20drone%20flattop%20that%20carries%20Iran's%20potent%20drone%20technology.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f56a6c3fe8d39283627897%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221227%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIran's%20Shahid%20Bahman%20Bagheri%20is%20a%20container%20ship%20converted%20into%20a%20drone%20flattop%20that%20carries%20Iran's%20potent%20technology.%3Cp%3EMaxar%2