al%20markets%20have%20slowed%20some%20corporate%20rights%20of%20passage%20like%20initial%20public%20offerings%2C%20sentiment%20around%20such%20transitions%2C%20for%20now%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20landed%20on%20%26quot%3Bpause%20versus%20delete.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20verb%20or%20a%20noun%2C%20pause%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20clutch%20term%20for%20some%20businesses%20navigating%20murky%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Trump's%20April%202%20Rose%20Garden%20speech%20detailing%20his%20intentions%20around%20the%20levies%2C%20the%20industrial%20technology%20company%20Acuity%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20with%20investors%20that%20it%20viewed%20tariffs%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20equivalent%20of%20a%20supply%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Neil%20Ashe%2C%20discussing%20the%20Atlanta%20company's%20lighting%20business%2C%20also%20said%20in%20the%20call%20that%20Acuity%20would%20%26quot%3Btake%20a%20pause%26quot%3B%20while%20it%20digested%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20word%20took%20center%20stage%20even%20before%20Trump%20announced%20the%20particulars%20of%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBGSF%2C%20a%20Plano%2C%20Texas%2C%20staffing%20firm%20that%20operates%20across%20the%20US%2C%20told%20investors%20in%20mid-March%20that%20it%20was%20seeing%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20activity%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20company's%20pipeline.%20CEO%20Beth%20Garvey%20also%20said%20in%20the%20earnings%20call%20that%20there%20had%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bslight%20pause%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20hopefulness%20that%20followed%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20but%20that%2C%20broadly%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20a%20cautious%20optimism%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenFirst%20Forest%20Products%2C%20a%20Canadian%20lumber%20company%2C%20also%20said%20in%20a%20mid-March%20investor%20call%20that%20it%20was%20prudent%20to%20%26quot%3Bpause%20certain%20elements%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20plans%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20soon-to-come%20tariffs%20and%20safeguard%20the%20company's%20balance%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e68ab5d3-197d-47f6-a45b-734dfa1a712e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaking%20it%20slow%20with%20big%20decisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20some%20companies%20might%20be%20pausing%20on%20pause%20as%20a%20turn%20of%20phrase%20is%20that%20it's%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20convey%20that%20they're%20taking%20a%20beat%20before%20making%20weighty%20decisions%20that%20could%20appear%20rash%20in%20only%20a%20few%20months'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERejiggering%20supply%20lines%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20often%20difficult%20and%20expensive%2C%20so%20CEOs%20don't%20tend%20to%20make%20those%20calls%20overnight%2C%20Erin%20McLaughlin%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20The%20Conference%20Board%2C%20told%20BI.%20Instead%2C%20she%20said%2C%20business%20leaders%20often%20make%20those%20decisions%20three%20to%20seven%20years%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcLaughlin%20said%20that%20even%20with%20a%20three-month%20halt%20to%20some%20tariffs%2C%20many%20medium%20and%20large%20businesses%20that%20make%20up%20the%20nonprofit's%20membership%20are%20still%20grappling%20with%20uncertainty%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20have%20decided%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20major%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20many%20CEOs%20want%20to%20better%20understand%20%26quot%3Bthe%20why%20and%20the%20end%20game%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20tariffs.%20Knowing%20that%2C%20McLaughlin%20said%2C%20could%20allow%20companies%20to%20ease%20up%20on%20the%20brakes%20and%20resume%20%26quot%3Ba%20normal%20decision-making%20paradigm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lasting%20delay%20could%20become%20problematic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%20Pick%20said%20that%20if%20adjusting%20to%20new%20economic%20conditions%20takes%20too%20long%2C%20the%20appetite%20for%20corporate%20activity%20such%20as%20mergers%20could%20fade%20to%20where%20%26quot%3Bthe%20pause%20effectively%20becomes%20a%20relook%20and%20the%20books%